<inglise> By exception: </inglise>
<eesti> Arvestatakse j&auml;rgmisi erandeid: </eesti>
<inglise> - The first quarter of reference starts on 5 January 1998 for Greece and Portugal and by consequence the last week of 1998 will be covered. </inglise>
<eesti> - Kreekas ja Portugalis algab esimene vaatluskvartal 5. jaanuaril 1998 ja seet&otilde;ttu h&otilde;lmatakse 1998. aasta viimane n&auml;dal. </eesti>
<inglise> - The fourth quarter of reference of 1998 will be formed by a block of 14 weeks for Denmark and Sweden. </inglise>
